wdi-BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD.def: Grants are defined as legally binding commitments that obligate a specific value of funds available for disbursement for which there is no repayment requirement. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD.name: Grants, excluding technical cooperation
wdi-BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD.source: World Bank, International Debt Statistics, and OECD.
